{
  "texts": [
    "They evaluated their approach on multiple tasks and showed that the augmented approach could improve the performance compared to the original bi-encoder.",
    "The process of this approach is illustrated in Figure 6 (Thakur et al., 2020).",
    "Figure 6: Augmented SBERT In-domain approach (Thakur et al., 2020) In this study, we have only unlabeled claim-pairs sentences (No annotated datasets).",
    "Therefore as shown in Figure 5, for fine-tuning SBERT the Augmented (Domain-Transfer) strategy was chosen.",
    "In this approach, in-domain sentence pairs are labeled with the cross-encoder."
  ]
}